# Project Structure Overview

This is a React + TypeScript application using Vite as the build tool. The main entry points and important files are:

- [main.tsx](mdc:src/main.tsx) - Application entry point
- [App.tsx](mdc:src/App.tsx) - Root component
- [routes.tsx](mdc:src/routes.tsx) - Application routing configuration

Key directories:
- `src/components/` - Reusable UI components
- `src/views/` - Page components
- `src/contexts/` - React context providers
- `src/hooks/` - Custom React hooks
- `src/services/` - API and external service integrations
- `src/lib/` - Utility functions and shared logic
- `src/types/` - TypeScript type definitions
- `src/assets/` - Static assets like images and icons

Configuration files:
- [vite.config.ts](mdc:vite.config.ts) - Vite build configuration
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) - TypeScript configuration
- [components.json](mdc:components.json) - UI components configuration

